pics": 227627, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 4296, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 693918, "username": "apollo007", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/apollo007", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ed76/9435/693918_mini.png?m=1728288909", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ed76/9435/693918_normal.png?m=1728288909", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ed76/9435/693918_large.png?m=1728288909", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ed76/9435/693918_xlarge.png?m=1728288909", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ed76/9435/693918_xlarge.png?m=1728288909", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ed76/9435/693918_xlarge.png?m=1728288909", "created": 1717387944, "last_modified": 1728288909}, "last_reply_by": "wy315700", "last_touched": 1737229938, "title": "请各位推荐一下：可以直接加自来水的加湿器？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1106093", "created": 1737188735, "deleted": 0, "content": "冬天太干燥了，家里湿度经常在 25%-35%。目前家里的加湿器，看着雾气挺大的，本来觉得还可以，但是发现抖音上都说加湿器用自来水会导致肺炎，建议用纯净水。搞得我现在都不敢用加湿器了，我就想，每天一大桶纯净水，是不是成本有点太高了？\r\n\r\n\r\n我整理了一下我的诉求：\r\n1. 可以直接用自来水（不是纯净水）\r\n2. 长期用不会导致肺炎\r\n3. 能方便加水（目前家里的加湿器，是底座分离的，加水比较方便。）\r\n4. 加湿效果好（家里有温湿度计，最好能在 40-50%湿度）\r\n\r\n请有这方面经验的兄弟们分享一下，谢谢大家，提前祝大家新年快乐！", "content_rendered": "<p>冬天太干燥了，家里湿度经常在 25%-35%。目前家里的加湿器，看着雾气挺大的，本来觉得还可以，但是发现抖音上都说加湿器用自来水会导致肺炎，建议用纯净水。搞得我现在都不敢用加湿器了，我就想，每天一大桶纯净水，是不是成本有点太高了？</p>\n<p>我整理了一下我的诉求：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>可以直接用自来水（不是纯净水）</li>\n<li>长期用不会导致肺炎</li>\n<li>能方便加水（目前家里的加湿器，是底座分离的，加水比较方便。）</li>\n<li>加湿效果好（家里有温湿度计，最好能在 40-50%湿度）</li>\n</ol>\n<p>请有这方面经验的兄弟们分享一下，谢谢大家，提前祝大家新年快乐！</p>\n", "last_modified": 1737189019, "replies": 44, "id": 1106093}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1733731195", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1733731195", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 65498, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1733731195", "stars": 9203, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 109689, "username": "evilStart", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/evilStart", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/23c3/aec1/109689_mini.png?m=1737181988", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/23c3/aec1/109689_normal.png?m=1737181988", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/23c3/aec1/109689_large.png?m=1737181988", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/23c3/aec1/109689_xlarge.png?m=1737181988", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/23c3/aec1/109689_xlarge.png?m=1737181988", "created": 1428417028, "last_modified": 1737181988}, "last_reply_by": "dream4ever", "last_touched": 1737242404, "title": "服了，天天都有 cursor 的帖子", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1106116", "created": 1737196746, "deleted": 0, "content": "觉得 cursor 太贵了，就想来搜搜有没有便宜的方法，结果一搜发现真的天天有各种帖子\r\n\r\n“cursor 太好用了”，“cursor 也没什么特别的”，“cursor 2 小时完成一个 app”，“被 cursor 气疯了”，无限循环。\r\n\r\n回复也都差不多：“几乎不用写代码了”，“啥都完成不了”，无限循环", "content_rendered": "<p>觉得 cursor 太贵了，就想来搜搜有没有便宜的方法，结果一搜发现真的天天有各种帖子</p>\n<p>“cursor 太好用了”，“cursor 也没什么特别的”，“cursor 2 小时完成一个 app”，“被 cursor 气疯了”，无限循环。</p>\n<p>回复也都差不多：“几乎不用写代码了”，“啥都完成不了”，无限循环</p>\n", "last_modified": 1737196746, "replies": 41, "id": 1106116}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1733731195", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1733731195", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 65498, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1733731195", "stars": 9203, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 47327, "username": "xhwdy26", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/xhwdy26", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6a30/4672/47327_mini.png?m=1610421534", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6a30/4672/47327_normal.png?m=1610421534", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6a30/4672/47327_large.png?m=1610421534", "created": 1382268735, "last_modified": 1610421534}, "last_reply_by": "qinxi", "last_touched": 1737233221, "title": "从微服务走向单体化", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1106152", "created": 1737210413, "deleted": 0, "content": "CEO 觉得微服务部署极其繁琐，什么 nacos 、mq 、redis 都好复杂，远不如零几年的开发一条龙从后台到前端那么简单。\r\n\r\n要求把十来个微服务(用户、订单、后台、网关等）合并成一个。\r\n\r\n简化部署，只一台机器搞定。\r\n\r\n试问，这种单体程序最后以怎样的方式崩溃。", "content_rendered": "<p>CEO 觉得微服务部署极其繁琐，什么 nacos 、mq 、redis 都好复杂，远不如零几年的开发一条龙从后台到前端那么简单。</p>\n<p>要求把十来个微服务(用户、订单、后台、网关等）合并成一个。</p>\n<p>简化部署，只一台机器搞定。</p>\n<p>试问，这种单体程序最后以怎样的方式崩溃。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1737210413, "replies": 36, "id": 1106152}]